Welcome to Interactive Stroop Test with Stimulus Duration.

column4: You will see text in 4 colors which are individually assigned to a key.

• Blue - key B
  • Red - key R
  • Green - key G
  • Yellow - key Y
Your task is to press the key as soon as possible when you see a color.
For example, you should press B key when seeing a word in color Blue, even if the word is Red.
Here is a tip, you can place your figures on the keys to have a better performance.
For instance, left middle figure on R; left index figure on B; right index figure on G; and right middle figure on Y
The experiment will start with a practice for you to be familiar with the task.
Press any key to begin the practice.

column3: The test will start. Remember to press the key according to the color rather than the word.
You can press S if you do not catch the blink color.
